41a86339ac95259b?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/38d5afa82294015541a86339ac95259b?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1422439185, "last_modified": 1660183937}, "last_reply_by": "yuruizhe", "last_touched": 1666203489, "title": "Type C 有无可能取消公母？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/888046", "created": 1666148741, "deleted": 0, "content": "USB Type-C 接口，最成功的地方在于取消了 USB 上下方向。对于老人家，特别好用。\r\n\r\n但是，存在公母的设计，即一凸一凹。一般情况下，手机和充电器，都是凹口，数据线两头凸，这个没问题。\r\n\r\n问题，如果遇到设备使用了凸口，那数据线需要一凸一凹，需要再配个两头凹的转接口。\r\n\r\n所以，有没有可能取消这个以凸一凹的设计？如果取消了，好像又要回到正反面的设计，例如两头都有凹凸口，实现互插…\r\n\r\n纯粹脑洞大开…", "content_rendered": "<p>USB Type-C 接口，最成功的地方在于取消了 USB 上下方向。对于老人家，特别好用。</p>\n<p>但是，存在公母的设计，即一凸一凹。一般情况下，手机和充电器，都是凹口，数据线两头凸，这个没问题。</p>\n<p>问题，如果遇到设备使用了凸口，那数据线需要一凸一凹，需要再配个两头凹的转接口。</p>\n<p>所以，有没有可能取消这个以凸一凹的设计？如果取消了，好像又要回到正反面的设计，例如两头都有凹凸口，实现互插…</p>\n<p>纯粹脑洞大开…</p>\n", "last_modified": 1666148741, "replies": 78, "id": 888046}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3636/6388/169_large.png?m=1586499345", "name": "appletv", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3636/6388/169_normal.png?m=1586499345", "title": "Apple TV", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/appletv", "topics": 78, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Apple TV", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3636/6388/169_mini.png?m=1586499345", "stars": 121, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 169, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 559700, "username": "misadonfdfl", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/misadonfdfl", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f13cddc77b5192c64afa1841b859c6f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f13cddc77b5192c64afa1841b859c6f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2f13cddc77b5192c64afa1841b859c6f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1635227408, "last_modified": 1635227408}, "last_reply_by": "dangyuluo", "last_touched": 1666202970, "title": "Apple TV 4K 出来了，有什么购买渠道？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/887994", "created": 1666141127, "deleted": 0, "content": "Apple TV 4K 就在今天发布了，有什么购买渠道吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>Apple TV 4K 就在今天发布了，有什么购买渠道吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1666141127, "replies": 75, "id": 887994}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_large.png?m=1347578950", "name": "icloud", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_normal.png?m=1347578950", "title": "iCloud", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/icloud", "topics": 938, "footer": null, "header": "Store contacts, calendars, photos, music, books, apps and more in the cloud and access them on all your devices.", "title_alternative": "iCloud", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_mini.png?m=1347578950", "stars": 182, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 430, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 564514, "username": "linchao10058", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/linchao10058", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_mini.png?m=1665680003", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_normal.png?m=1665680003", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_large.png?m=1665680003", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_xlarge.png?m=1665680003", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_xlarge.png?m=1665680003", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a7ff/c3d8/564514_xlarge.png?m=1665680003", "created": 1638858163, "last_modified": 1665680003}, "last_reply_by": "mikeven", "last_touched": 1666206279, "title": "出于便捷,安全,隐私方面的考虑，大家觉得到底有没有必要从国区云上贵州转到美区 iCloud 呢？未来可能会发生哪些问题？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/888067", "created": 1666151910, "deleted": 0, "content": "至少在目前我是考虑终生只用 iPhone 和其他 Apple 设备的，由于资料很多，也在不断让更多家人加入 Apple 家族，这样让很多问题变得复杂，所以对此问题我很重视，出于便捷,安全,隐私方面的考虑，大家觉得到底有没有必要从国区云上贵州转到美区 iCloud 呢？未来可能会发生哪些未知问题？", "content_rendered": "<p>至少在目前我是考虑终生只用 iPhone 和其他 Apple 设备的，由于资料很多，也在不断让更多家人加入 Apple 家族，这样让很多问题变得复杂，所以对此问题我很重视，出于便捷,安全,隐私方面的考虑，大家觉得到底有没有必要从国区云上贵州转到美区 iCloud 呢？未来可能会发生哪些未知问题？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1666151910, "replies": 68, "id": 888067}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_large.png?m=1625409262", "name": "software", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_normal.png?m=1625409262", "title": "软件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/software", "topics": 574, "footer": "", "header": "关于软件使用的日常讨论", "title_alternative": "Software", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/41ae/36ec/417_mini.png?m=1625409262", "stars": 286, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 417, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 213963, "username": "yuhuanxi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhuanxi", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/71785256fd7e810da6973937c1955ad6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/71785256fd7e810da6973937c1955ad6?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/71785256fd7e810da6973937c1955ad6?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1486531495, "last_modified": 1660269623}, "last_reply_by": "future0906", "last_touched": 1666199167, "title": "用过很多笔记，最终回到了 obsidian", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/888029", "created": 1666146184, "deleted": 0, "content": "在重度使用 obsidian 的两个多月里，发现越来越爱上这个软件了。\r\n\r\n我的笔记系统经历了以下几个历程：\r\n\r\nnotion->flomo->craft->obsidian->notion->obsidian\r\n\r\n兜兜转转又回到了 obsidian ，主要还是看重了数据本地化，并且 obsidian 的各种插件实在太强大了，要啥有啥。\r\n\r\n用 obsidian 配合 iCloud + obsidian Git 插件，这感觉很爽啊，相当于有了近乎实时的同步+备份+历史版本的功能，加上 obsidian 的各种插件，日常使用真感觉爽的飞起。\r\n\r\n之前看到有帖子说 iCloud 丢数据的问题，备忘录啥的可能不见了。所以我现在基本上 [证件]  [资料] 等重要的东西全都在 obsidian 上开一个文件夹存起来，ji shi iCloud 数据都清空了，上了 Git 后就不怕这个问题了。\r\n\r\n如果还在观望笔记的同学，可以试试 obsidian 。", "content_rendered": "<p>在重度使用 obsidian 的两个多月里，发现越来越爱上这个软件了。</p>\n<p>我的笔记系统经历了以下几个历程：</p>\n<p>notion-&gt;flomo-&gt;craft-&gt;obsidian-&gt;notion-&gt;obsidian</p>\n<p>兜兜转转又回到了 obsidian ，主要还是看重了数据本地化，并且 obsidian 的各种插件实在太强大了，要啥有啥。</p>\n<p>用 obsidian 配合 iCloud + obsidian Git 插件，这感觉很爽啊，相当于有了近乎实时的同步+备份+历史版本的功能，加上 obsidian 的各种插件，日常使用真感觉爽的飞起。</p>\n<p>之前看到有帖子说 iCloud 丢数据的问题，备忘录啥的可能不见了。所以我现在基本上 [证件]  [资料] 等重要的东西全都在 obsidian 上开一个文件夹存起来，ji shi iCloud 数据都清空了，上了 Git 后就不怕这个问题了。</p>\n<p>如果还在观望笔记的同学，可以试试 obsidian 。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1666155044, "replies": 68, "id": 888029}]